    EDAC/ie31200: Add two more Intel Coffee Lake processors for EDAC support
    
    Host Device IDs (DID0) correspond to:
    - Intel Xeon E-2176M
    - Intel Xeon E-2186M
    - Intel Xeon E-2254ME
    - Intel Xeon E-2254ML
    - Intel Xeon E-2276M
    - Intel Xeon E-2276ME
    - Intel Xeon E-2276ML
    - Intel Xeon E-2286M
    
    See documentation:
    * Intel® Xeon® E-2100 and E-2200 Processor Product Family Datasheet, Vol. 2
        * https://www.intel.com/content/dam/www/public/us/en/documents/datasheets/xeon-e-2100-datasheet-vol-2.pdf

